Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.46,0:01:06.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打烊时间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:06.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Closing time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.65,0:01:09.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一天最快乐的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.65,0:01:09.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the happiest time of the day
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.05,0:01:11.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打烊时间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.05,0:01:11.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Closing time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.30,0:01:14.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一天最悲伤的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.30,0:01:14.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the saddest time of the day
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.77,0:01:19.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是个蟹黄堡肉饼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.77,0:01:19.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.77,0:01:22.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又冷又硬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.77,0:01:22.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's cold and hard
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.00,0:01:24.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能好多年前就滚到那里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.00,0:01:24.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This could have rolled there years ago
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.05,0:01:26.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事了  小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.05,0:01:26.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There, there, little one
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.87,0:01:28.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一生的旅途就快结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.87,0:01:28.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your journey is almost over
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.82,0:01:33.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.82,0:01:33.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.20,0:01:36.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人想扔掉一块肉饼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.20,0:01:36.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Someone tried to throw away a patty
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.30,0:01:41.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小气夹夹机已为您立省五分二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.30,0:01:41.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pinch-o-matic has saved you 5.2 cents
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.12,0:01:42.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:42.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.40,0:01:44.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可是在烤架底下找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:44.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I found that under the grill
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.22,0:01:47.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天把肉饼放蟹黄堡里让客人吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.22,0:01:47.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And tomorrow a customer will find it under his bun
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.87,0:01:48.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:48.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.42,0:01:50.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它都过期了  冷冰冰的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:50.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's old and it's cold
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.48,0:01:52.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且发满了霉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.48,0:01:52.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and so very full of mold
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.09,0:01:55.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那肉饼没卖出去就不准再做
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:55.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not to make another patty until that one is sold
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.61,0:01:56.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:56.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.67,0:01:58.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,第二天
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.01,0:01:59.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上菜了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:01:59.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Order up, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.57,0:02:00.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.57,0:02:00.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.07,0:02:05.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.07,0:02:05.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.10,0:02:07.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能来个少一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:07.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,can I get one with less
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.15,0:02:08.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,雾气的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.15,0:02:08.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,fog
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.85,0:02:10.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:10.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.00,0:02:11.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是蟹老板要求的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.00,0:02:11.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs's orders
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.82,0:02:12.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,管他的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.82,0:02:12.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.22,0:02:14.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.22,0:02:14.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you are, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.05,0:02:15.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一份蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.05,0:02:15.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,one Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.10,0:02:20.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就不明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.10,0:02:20.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't understand
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.80,0:02:22.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经好几周都没客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:22.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We haven't had a customer in weeks
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.31,0:02:25.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道是不是因为换了餐具垫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.31,0:02:25.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's the new placemats
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.37,0:02:25.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:25.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.82,0:02:27.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,餐具垫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.82,0:02:27.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Placemats?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.75,0:02:29.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你发什么神经
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:29.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you lost your mind?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.52,0:02:30.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都要怪那个过期肉饼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.52,0:02:30.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's that old patty
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.96,0:02:33.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还想拿它卖给大家吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:33.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you keep trying to sell to everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.11,0:02:34.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它早都变质了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:34.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's gone bad
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.92,0:02:36.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,变质了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:36.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gone bad?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.07,0:02:37.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一派胡言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.07,0:02:37.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's nonsense
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.30,0:02:38.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿过来  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:38.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bring it here, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.97,0:02:42.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛关笼子里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:42.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why is it in a cage?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.39,0:02:43.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为它吼我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:43.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because it growled at me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.77,0:02:51.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你俩参加海军肯定没法战斗到底
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:51.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You two would have never have lasted in the navy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.20,0:02:52.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看你到底多坏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:52.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see how bad you are
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.86,0:02:56.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:56.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.92,0:02:57.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:02:57.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.87,0:03:01.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:01.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stay
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.82,0:03:03.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真乖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:03.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That a girl
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.73,0:03:05.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.73,0:03:05.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There, there
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.49,0:03:07.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:07.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.30,0:03:08.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:08.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good enough to eat
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.92,0:03:12.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:12.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.55,0:03:13.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有救护船
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.55,0:03:13.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,An ambulance
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.53,0:03:15.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.53,0:03:15.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, then
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:15.96,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(708,472)}急救
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.07,0:03:18.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:18.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.60,0:03:21.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:21.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.45,0:03:24.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要把那个肉饼包好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:24.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make sure you wrap up that patty
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:27.93,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(236,634)}手术室
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.02,0:03:26.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还没吃完
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:26.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not finished with it yet
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.56,0:03:31.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  真是虚惊一场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:31.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Mr. Krabs, you gave us quite a scare
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.87,0:03:33.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我应该会没事吧  医生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:33.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So I'm going to be okay, doc?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.83,0:03:36.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是不相信我说的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:36.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if you don't want to take my word for it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.13,0:03:37.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就直接看你病历好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:37.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let's just check your chart
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.22,0:03:39.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.22,0:03:39.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see here
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.30,0:03:41.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:41.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.19,0:03:43.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.19,0:03:43.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.11,0:03:45.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.11,0:03:45.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is terrible
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.67,0:03:47.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事吧  医生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.67,0:03:47.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything okay, doc?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.40,0:03:48.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.40,0:03:48.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.79,0:03:51.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可不是好兆头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:51.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not a good sign
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.00,0:03:57.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了  是飞天魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:57.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, it's the Flying Dutchman
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.85,0:04:02.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尤金蟹  你的死期到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.85,0:04:02.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eugene Krabs, your time has come
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.39,0:04:06.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不是尤金蟹  我是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.39,0:04:06.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not Eugene Krabs, I'm, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.05,0:04:07.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哈罗德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:07.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Harold
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.28,0:04:08.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哈罗德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:08.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Harold, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.62,0:04:09.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.62,0:04:09.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flower
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.95,0:04:10.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:10.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.77,0:04:12.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定走错病房了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:12.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must have the wrong room
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.97,0:04:14.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请问一下  护士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.97,0:04:14.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, nurse?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.60,0:04:15.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:15.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.67,0:04:18.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在找尤金蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:18.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for Eugene Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.58,0:04:20.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他就在那边那间病房
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.58,0:04:20.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's in that room, right there
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.22,0:04:22.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  那间是哈罗德小花的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:22.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, that's Harold Flower's room
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.88,0:04:24.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哈罗德小花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:24.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Harold Flower?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.49,0:04:25.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老螃蟹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:25.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.97,0:04:28.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你自以为能骗得过飞天魔鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:28.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You thought you could fool the Flying Dutchman?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.78,0:04:30.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想找我干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:30.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you want from me?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.87,0:04:32.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来送你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:32.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm here to escort you
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.67,0:04:36.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前往所有海底恶棍的安息之处
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:36.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to the resting place of all bad undersea folk
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.29,0:04:40.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,戴维琼斯柜子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:40.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Davy Jones's locker
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.67,0:04:42.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,戴维琼斯柜子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:42.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Davy Jones's locker?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.40,0:04:44.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凭什么要过去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:44.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to go there?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.12,0:04:45.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又没干坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.12,0:04:45.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not a bad crab
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.03,0:04:48.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是你很小气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.03,0:04:48.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you were cheap
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.55,0:04:51.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小气就是坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:51.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and being cheap is a terrible thing
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.27,0:04:52.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一站
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:52.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next stop
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.67,0:04:55.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,戴维琼斯柜子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:55.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Davy Jones's locker
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:04:58.77,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(662,270)}戴维琼斯
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.37,0:05:01.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:01.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here we are
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.45,0:05:06.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么有股臭味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:06.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why does it smell so foul?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.28,0:05:08.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,戴维琼斯常常健身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:08.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Davy Jones works out a lot
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.92,0:05:10.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些是他的袜子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:10.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These are his socks
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.93,0:05:11.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.93,0:05:11.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get in
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.77,0:05:16.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你了  飞天魔鬼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:16.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, Mr. Dutchman
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.55,0:05:19.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不想进去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.55,0:05:19.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want to go in there
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.82,0:05:21.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我什么都愿意做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:21.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.92,0:05:24.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你再给我一次机会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:24.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, give me another chance
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.74,0:05:26.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得了吧  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.74,0:05:26.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.42,0:05:28.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有尊严一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.42,0:05:28.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,show a little dignity
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.71,0:05:30.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.71,0:05:30.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mommy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.87,0:05:33.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了好了  别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.87,0:05:33.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, all right, stop your crying
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.72,0:05:35.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这就再给你一次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:35.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll give you another chance
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.62,0:05:38.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但你必须一直大方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.62,0:05:38.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you must always be generous
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.65,0:05:40.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不许小气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:40.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never cheap
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.77,0:05:42.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我以水手的身份向你保证
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:42.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have my word as a sailor
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.57,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(418,446)}停业
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.40,0:05:48.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板的鼻毛剪子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:48.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs' nose hair clippers
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.66,0:05:50.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我应该用得上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:50.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could use these
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.20,0:05:51.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  不应该随便乱翻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:51.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, you shouldn't be going
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.98,0:05:53.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.98,0:05:53.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,through Mr. Krabs' belongings
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.80,0:05:56.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他绝对不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:56.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He won't like it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.54,0:05:59.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  医生的话我早告诉你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:59.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I told you what the doctor said
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.54,0:06:02.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板回不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:02.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs isn't coming back
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.00,0:06:02.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:02.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, keep quiet
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.84,0:06:04.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样才听得见保险柜锁声
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:04.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I can hear the tumblers in his safe
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.51,0:06:05.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:05.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.10,0:06:08.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:08.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, I knew it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.32,0:06:09.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:09.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're alive
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.55,0:06:10.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  快看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:10.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, look
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.72,0:06:12.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:12.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.17,0:06:14.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是棒得跟假的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.17,0:06:14.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't this too good to be true?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.82,0:06:16.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:16.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it was
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.06,0:06:17.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你们说  小子们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:17.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.25,0:06:19.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大病一场让我思绪万千
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:19.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,being sick made me do a lot of thinking
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.40,0:06:21.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这一生都在为钱奔波
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:21.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My whole life has been about money
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.38,0:06:23.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,省钱  赚钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:23.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Saving money, collecting money
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.10,0:06:25.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摸钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:25.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,touching money
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.58,0:06:28.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们应该都懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.58,0:06:28.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you get the picture
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.95,0:06:29.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但以后不会了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:29.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But no more
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.74,0:06:31.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们眼前的是全新向善
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:31.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're looking at the new, improved
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.37,0:06:33.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不再小气的蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:33.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,non-cheap Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:36.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(794,166)}盛大重新开业
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:36.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(966,792)}免费
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:36.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(498,792)}购买
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.32,0:06:36.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.32,0:06:36.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome, all, welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:37.79,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(528,412)}庆贺好时光
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.10,0:06:40.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:40.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, little one
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.80,0:06:42.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,手上拿的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:42.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What you got there?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.04,0:06:43.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:43.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.57,0:06:46.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:46.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course you do
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.22,0:06:48.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道是什么意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:48.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know what that means, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.50,0:06:49.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不会饿肚子了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:49.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't go hungry?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.87,0:06:51.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:51.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, silly
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.55,0:06:52.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,意思就是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:52.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It means
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.35,0:06:54.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免费玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.35,0:06:54.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,free toy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.80,0:06:56.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:06:56.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, thanks, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.87,0:06:59.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还以为你是个超级小气鬼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.87,0:06:59.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought you were a cheap old tightwad
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.00,0:07:01.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原先确实是  孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:01.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was, son, I was
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.22,0:07:02.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免费玩具大家有份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.22,0:07:02.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Free toys for everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.90,0:07:04.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,外加免费续杯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:04.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And free refills
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:12.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(444,228)}活在当下
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.82,0:07:07.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:07.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.90,0:07:09.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:09.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, where's Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.55,0:07:11.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他好像是在你办公室休息什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:11.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's taking one of those break things in your office
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.71,0:07:13.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  员工休息室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.71,0:07:13.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean the "employee lounge"
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.72,0:07:18.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:18.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.60,0:07:21.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  我蟹黄堡掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:21.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but I dropped my Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.15,0:07:22.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以再来一个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:22.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could I get another one?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.47,0:07:23.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.47,0:07:23.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.15,0:07:23.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:23.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.18,0:07:25.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王店规明确指出
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:25.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Krusty Krab policy clearly states
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:29.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(716,276)}店规
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.80,0:07:27.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一旦汉堡送达顾客
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:27.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"that once the burger has reached the customer
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.33,0:07:29.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就由其自负
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.33,0:07:29.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it is his/her responsibility"
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.26,0:07:30.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:30.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.30,0:07:31.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那店规都作古了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:31.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the old policy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.97,0:07:33.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快回去做个新的出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:33.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now run back and bring out a fresh one
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.67,0:07:34.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.67,0:07:34.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.93,0:07:36.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉让你误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:36.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry about the confusion
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.29,0:07:37.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要免费玩具不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:37.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Free toy?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.51,0:07:39.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尤金  好兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:39.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eugene, my man
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.51,0:07:41.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.51,0:07:41.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.00,0:07:42.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,休息得怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:42.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's the break coming?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.42,0:07:44.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该再休息几小时就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:44.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Should be over in a couple of hours
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.44,0:07:46.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叫海绵宝宝给我送蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:46.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have SpongeBob send back a patty
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.18,0:07:47.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有冰茶行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.18,0:07:47.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and an iced tea, will you?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.57,0:07:49.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:49.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure thing, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.15,0:07:50.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放松一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:50.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take it easy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.95,0:07:53.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喜欢就餐期间看的电影吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:53.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you enjoying your in-meal movie?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.82,0:07:56.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这电影连院线都还没上过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:56.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This movie hasn't even been in the theaters yet
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.65,0:07:59.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不遗余力服务我尊贵的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.65,0:07:59.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No expense spared for my valued customers
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.33,0:08:02.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看他们表情多快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:02.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at all those happy faces
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.65,0:08:05.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大方的感觉真好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:05.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It sure does feel good to be generous
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.38,0:08:07.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你邮件来了  尤金
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:07.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's your mail, Eugene
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.30,0:08:08.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:08.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.47,0:08:09.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你休息得挺爽嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.47,0:08:09.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You look rested
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.55,0:08:13.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  上班睡觉让我容光焕发
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:13.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, these naps at work are doing wonders for me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.27,0:08:14.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,信用卡账单
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:14.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Credit card bills
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.75,0:08:16.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这东西果然还是来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.75,0:08:16.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I knew this was coming
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.52,0:08:18.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看损失了多少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.52,0:08:18.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see what the damage is
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:21.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(364,354)}账单
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.37,0:08:20.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才一万块
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:20.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only $10,000
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.22,0:08:21.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也没多糟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:21.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not so bad
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.99,0:08:24.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从今天的利润减掉就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.99,0:08:24.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just subtract it from today's profit
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.31,0:08:26.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:26.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.39,0:08:28.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面也没钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.39,0:08:28.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there's no money in here
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.52,0:08:30.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太美妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.52,0:08:30.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How delightful
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.32,0:08:33.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  我有点不放心蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:33.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, I'm worried about Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.46,0:08:34.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:34.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me, too
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.62,0:08:35.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样还怎么领工资
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.62,0:08:35.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how are we going to get paid?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.82,0:08:40.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  你还真能心平气和接受破产
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:40.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, Mr. Krabs, you sure are taking total bankruptcy well
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.57,0:08:42.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一场噩梦罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.57,0:08:42.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just a bad dream
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.37,0:08:43.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我反正马上就要醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:43.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll wake up soon
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.98,0:08:46.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,梦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.98,0:08:46.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Dream"?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.66,0:08:47.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.66,0:08:47.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.72,0:08:49.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还在住院
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.72,0:08:49.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm still in the hospital
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.42,0:08:51.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,睡得可香了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:51.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sleeping like a baby
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.60,0:08:53.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你今早就出院了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.60,0:08:53.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You checked out of the hospital this morning
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.80,0:08:54.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是账单
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:54.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's the bill
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.77,0:08:55.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.77,0:08:55.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.70,0:08:57.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没做梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.70,0:08:57.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm awake?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.88,0:09:06.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准再续杯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.88,0:09:06.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more refills
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:07.35,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(890,440)}免费汽水
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.93,0:09:10.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玩具还回来  吃霸王餐的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.93,0:09:10.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me back them toys, you freeloaders
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.39,0:09:13.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,演完了  小气鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:13.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Show's over, cheapskate
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.65,0:09:21.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我今天真幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:21.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's my lucky day
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.08,0:09:22.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一分钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:22.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A penny
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.07,0:09:24.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你运气全没了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.07,0:09:24.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your luck just ran out
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.61,0:09:25.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟  轻一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.61,0:09:25.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, man, ease back
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.85,0:09:27.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都快弄断我胳膊了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.85,0:09:27.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're crushing my arm
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.22,0:09:29.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,交出那分钱  不然马上让你断臂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.22,0:09:29.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Unhand that penny or the arm comes off
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.95,0:09:36.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚刚的表现小气得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.95,0:09:36.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That little display of parsimonious penny pinching
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.80,0:09:41.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我要把你关回戴维琼斯柜子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:38.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just earned you a nice little spot
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:41.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in Davy Jones's locker
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.01,0:09:42.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:42.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for eternity
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.80,0:09:44.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不小气  我可大方了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.80,0:09:44.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not cheap, I'm generous
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.93,0:09:47.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚就为一分钱差点让别人断臂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:47.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You almost tore a man's arm off for a penny
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.00,0:09:49.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多谢帮倒忙  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:49.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.05,0:09:50.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你果然没让我失望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.05,0:09:50.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew I could count on you
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.01,0:09:53.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.01,0:09:53.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, a deal's a deal
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.67,0:09:54.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出发
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:54.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.76,0:09:57.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先给我等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.76,0:09:57.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait just a burger-flipping second
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.66,0:10:01.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁这么大胆  敢跟飞天魔鬼顶嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:10:01.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who dares back-sass the Flying Dutchman?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.25,0:10:02.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.25,0:10:02.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That would be me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.77,0:10:05.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵顶嘴宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.77,0:10:05.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob Back-sass Pants
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.35,0:10:07.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你抓错螃蟹了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.35,0:10:07.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I say you got the wrong crab
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.70,0:10:10.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位蟹老板是最大方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.70,0:10:10.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This Mr. Krabs is the most generous
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.08,0:10:12.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最宽宏大量  最不吝啬的螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:12.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,big-hearted, non-skinflinted crab
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.73,0:10:13.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全海洋就他一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.73,0:10:13.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the whole sea
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.25,0:10:17.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他会就为了几块钱出卖你的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:17.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He'd sell your soul for a couple of bucks
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.67,0:10:20.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我用我灵魂打赌  他肯定不会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:20.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd bet my soul he wouldn't
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.17,0:10:21.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就来赌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:21.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got yourself a bet
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.00,0:10:23.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:23.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.28,0:10:24.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会让你留下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.28,0:10:24.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll let you stay
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.59,0:10:27.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但你要先帮我打赌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.59,0:10:27.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but first help me settle a bet
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.10,0:10:30.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果只有两个选择  一个是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:30.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you had to choose between SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.05,0:10:32.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,另一个是我口袋里的所有钱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.05,0:10:32.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and all the money in my pocket
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.05,0:10:34.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你会怎么选
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:34.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,which would you take?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.40,0:10:35.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看情况
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:35.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That depends
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.48,0:10:36.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这钱有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:36.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how much money we talking about?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.60,0:10:37.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:37.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.92,0:10:40.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,六毛二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.92,0:10:40.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sixty-two cents
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.07,0:10:40.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱我收了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:40.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take the money
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.22,0:10:42.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.22,0:10:42.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.45,0:10:44.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿去吧  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:44.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.10,0:10:46.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,六毛二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:46.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sixty-two cents
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.31,0:10:49.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一站  戴维琼斯柜子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.31,0:10:49.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next stop Davy Jones's locker
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.65,0:10:55.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥你看  有钱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:55.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, Squidward, money
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.30,0:10:58.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  我竟然会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:58.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, I can't believe I'm saying this
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.00,0:11:02.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么可以拿海绵宝宝换六毛二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:11:02.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but how could you trade SpongeBob for 62 cents?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.45,0:11:04.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说我本来还能换更多钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.45,0:11:04.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You think I could have gotten more?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.07,0:11:07.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他为你挺身而出  结果你把他给卖了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.07,0:11:07.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He stuck up for you and you sold him out
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.02,0:11:09.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该为自己感到羞耻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:09.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You should be ashamed of yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.72,0:11:12.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我干了什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.72,0:11:12.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What have I done?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.27,0:11:15.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再给我一次机会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:15.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want another chance
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.10,0:11:17.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我什么教训都没学到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:17.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't learn anything
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.55,0:11:19.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还失去了我最棒的煎炸厨师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:19.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I lost my best fry cook
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.29,0:11:23.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不要这臭钱了  我要海绵宝宝回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:23.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want this foul money, I want SpongeBob back
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.06,0:11:29.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给  带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.06,0:11:29.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, take him back
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.27,0:11:30.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你听见我刚刚说钱的话了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:30.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You heard what I said about the money?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.96,0:11:32.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听你说什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:32.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heard what you said?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.57,0:11:35.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这家伙吵得我集中不了注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.57,0:11:35.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I couldn't hear myself thinking with this one around
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.75,0:11:37.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才抓了他三十秒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:37.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I only had him for 30 seconds
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.96,0:11:39.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他就一会儿捉水母
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:39.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and it's jellyfishing this
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.64,0:11:41.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一会儿美人鱼战士的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.64,0:11:41.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and Mermaidman that
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.60,0:11:43.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不还回去怎么得了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:43.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What "not giving him back"?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.24,0:11:44.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有他简直是活受罪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.24,0:11:44.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's a fate worse than death
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.83,0:11:45.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自己带网
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.83,0:11:45.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bring your own net
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.76,0:11:47.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他现在是你的问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:47.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's your problem now
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.80,0:11:54.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先前把你卖了换零钱的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.80,0:11:54.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,About trading you for pocket change
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.80,0:11:56.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用多说  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:56.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say no more, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.65,0:11:58.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都是为了蟹堡王着想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:11:58.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You did it for the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.80,0:12:00.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这情况也会把你卖了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:00.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I would have done the same thing
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.50,0:12:01.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:01.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You would have?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.73,0:12:02.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.73,0:12:02.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.30,0:12:12.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞天魔鬼家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.30,0:12:12.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dutchman's residence
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.78,0:12:13.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我先前说到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.78,0:12:13.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, as I was saying
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.52,0:12:14.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱俩要多逛逛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:14.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you and me got to hang out more
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.45,0:12:15.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你哪天晚上有空
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.45,0:12:15.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, what nights are good for you
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.36,0:12:16.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我下面几晚都行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:16.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here are the nights that are good for me
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.25,0:12:17.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,周一二三四五六日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:16.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Monday, Tuesday, Wednesday
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:17.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thursday, Friday, Saturday, Sunday
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.88,0:12:18.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得上班
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:18.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gotta work
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.42,0:12:19.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,工位在蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:19.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I work at the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.21,0:12:20.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好朋友是派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:20.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My best friend is Patrick
Dialogue: 3,0:12:20.09,0:12:20.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是粉的
Dialogue: 2,0:12:20.09,0:12:20.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's pink
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:23.80,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(359,349)}我出了事故
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:25.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz27.79\pos(335.802,504)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:29.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:27.39,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz27.79\pos(377.802,584)}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:29.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.67\pos(399.802,298)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:31.35,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.1\pos(285.802,414)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:31.35,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.1\pos(469.802,712)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:31.35,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:34.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1020,794)}沙山
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:44.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(718,424)}死亡
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.40,0:12:44.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:44.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got dead again
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.99,0:12:46.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,垃圾游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:46.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This game stinks
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.00,0:12:53.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧  所以你必须时时刻刻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:53.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See, that's why you must always
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.38,0:12:54.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心注意高山
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.38,0:12:54.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,pay attention to the mountain
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.92,0:12:57.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听着你呢  高山
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:57.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm listening to you, mountain
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.57,0:13:00.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别吃黄沙  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.57,0:13:00.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't eat the yellow sand, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.20,0:13:01.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊对  我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:01.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, I forgot
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.30,0:13:06.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  看我表演暴躁章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:06.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sandy, watch me do the "Grouchy Squidward"
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.59,0:13:08.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别用我名字称呼你的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.59,0:13:08.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop naming moves after me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.76,0:13:11.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都是白痴  只有我不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:11.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everybody's an idiot except for me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.68,0:13:12.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本来就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:12.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it's true
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.02,0:13:20.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:20.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.07,0:13:21.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心那棵树
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:21.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look out for that tree
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.75,0:13:26.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心  一切全在掌控之中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.75,0:13:26.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, everything's under control
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.49,0:13:30.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我是专家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:30.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'cause I'm an expert
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.90,0:13:32.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.90,0:13:32.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's funny
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.78,0:13:34.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这山被谁倒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:34.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,someone turned the mountain upside-down
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.32,0:13:40.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  用屁股着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.32,0:13:40.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, land on your bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.38,0:13:43.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以缓冲坠落带来的冲击力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:43.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It'll cushion the impact of the fall
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.39,0:13:45.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:45.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.50,0:13:47.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  另一个屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:47.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, your other bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.12,0:13:49.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就不能到别处去犯傻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.12,0:13:49.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you have to be stupid somewhere else?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.10,0:13:50.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要到四点才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:50.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not until four
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.93,0:13:54.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定很疼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:54.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's got to hurt
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.92,0:13:56.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来一遍  我刚没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.92,0:13:56.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do it again, I wasn't looking
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:13:57.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(510,872)}医院
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.49,0:14:00.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来你的臀大肌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.49,0:14:00.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it looks like your gluteus maximus
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:13:59.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(856,550)}急诊
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.79,0:14:02.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经痊愈了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.79,0:14:02.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,has made a full recovery
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.30,0:14:04.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我什么已经什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:04.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My what has a what now?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.27,0:14:05.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你屁股康复了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.27,0:14:05.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your butt's all better
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:06.86,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\pos(614,232)}X{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}光
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.45,0:14:06.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,实在是神奇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.45,0:14:06.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's really quite amazing
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.86,0:14:09.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们花了二十小时才成功拼了回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:09.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It took 20 hours to put it all back together
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.10,0:14:12.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过缝合钉用完了  只好换了胶水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:11.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We actually ran out of staples
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:12.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and had to use a glue stick
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.60,0:14:13.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  你简直是个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:13.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep, you're a
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.64,0:14:16.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幸运幸运幸运幸运幸运幸运儿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.64,0:14:16.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,lucky, lucky, lucky, lucky, lucky, luck-boy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.91,0:14:18.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是从现在起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:18.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But from now on
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.40,0:14:19.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你必须多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:19.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to be more careful
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.92,0:14:21.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一旦再次那样受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:21.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One more injury like that
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.55,0:14:24.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,后果就有可能跟那边那位可怜虫一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:24.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you could wind up like that poor creature there
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.64,0:14:26.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,戴上铁屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.64,0:14:26.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In the Iron Butt
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.47,0:14:29.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  痒死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:29.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, man, it itches
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.63,0:14:32.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听见医生的话了吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.63,0:14:32.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You heard the doctor, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.37,0:14:35.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一旦再次那样受伤  就得戴铁屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:35.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,one more injury like that and it's the Iron Butt
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.97,0:14:37.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我那时太大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:37.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been too careless back there
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.90,0:14:40.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从现在起  我要无时无刻保护好屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.90,0:14:40.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,From now on I am on round-the-clock butt patrol
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.74,0:14:43.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,离我屁股远点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:43.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Step away from the backside
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.33,0:14:44.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我警告你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.33,0:14:44.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm warning you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.40,0:14:45.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你什么毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:45.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's your problem?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.60,0:14:47.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:47.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was close
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.69,0:14:48.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.69,0:14:48.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.74,0:14:49.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过来一起打球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:49.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you join us?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.63,0:14:50.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来一个球员就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.63,0:14:50.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We need an extra player
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.62,0:14:52.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接得好啊  珀西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:52.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice catch, Percy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.01,0:14:55.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.01,0:14:55.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.65,0:14:57.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要来试试这个  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.65,0:14:57.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got to try this, dude
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.70,0:14:59.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总算要凑齐人头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:14:59.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We finally got enough people
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.05,0:15:01.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起组成七里长的拍屁股大队了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.05,0:15:01.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for a seven-mile spanking machine
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.34,0:15:06.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.34,0:15:06.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.62,0:15:10.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,队伍是从这排吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:10.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is this where the line starts?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.22,0:15:12.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,屁股在外面不安全
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:12.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My butt is not safe out here
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.40,0:15:15.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管哪个部位都不安全
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.40,0:15:15.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No part of me is safe
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.52,0:15:20.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  牛仔骑大马
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:20.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, ride 'em, cowboy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.60,0:15:26.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:26.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.47,0:15:34.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚太好玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:34.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was fun
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.87,0:15:38.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  准备好再去滑沙了没
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:38.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob, you ready to go sand-boarding again?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.92,0:15:39.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:39.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.23,0:15:41.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朋友们好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.23,0:15:41.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, friends
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.70,0:15:43.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在外面的世界还开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.70,0:15:43.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enjoying the outside world?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.63,0:15:46.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你那样坐地板上干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:44.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What y'all doing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:46.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sitting in the middle of the floor like that?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.85,0:15:48.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,度过余生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.85,0:15:48.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Living out the remainder of my life
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.65,0:15:50.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万事平安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.65,0:15:50.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in safety
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.12,0:15:52.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,聪明点的都会跟我一起闭门不出
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:52.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you guys were smart, you would join me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.45,0:15:54.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那场事故让我醒悟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:54.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That accident made me realize
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.17,0:15:55.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,了解到外面的世界分外危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.17,0:15:55.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that it's dangerous out there
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.82,0:15:57.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而我是一名幸运儿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.82,0:15:57.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was one of the lucky ones
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.45,0:15:58.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一名幸存者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:15:58.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a survivor
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.75,0:15:59.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我就此决定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.75,0:15:59.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And so I've simply decided
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.92,0:16:01.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我绝对不会再出家门一步
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.92,0:16:01.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am never leaving my house again
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.77,0:16:03.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好一个疯话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:03.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's crazy talk
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.17,0:16:04.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那又不是疯话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:04.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not crazy talk
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.70,0:16:06.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这才是疯话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.70,0:16:06.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is crazy talk
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.86,0:16:12.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.86,0:16:12.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.33,0:16:13.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.33,0:16:13.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.82,0:16:15.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星说得才对  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:15.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick's right, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.15,0:16:16.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都看到我先前的下场了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.15,0:16:16.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You saw what happened to me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.52,0:16:18.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下次出事  伤的可不只会是屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.52,0:16:18.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and next time it won't just be my butt
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.77,0:16:21.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还会是胳肢窝  或者额头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.77,0:16:21.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it'll be my armpit or my forehead
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.04,0:16:22.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者另一个胳肢窝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:22.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or your other armpit
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.62,0:16:24.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本就不该违背自然规律
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:24.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was wrong to go against nature
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.74,0:16:26.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可是海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.74,0:16:26.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.00,0:16:26.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在胡思乱想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.00,0:16:26.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What was I thinking?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.97,0:16:27.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:27.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Walking
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.87,0:16:29.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的同类天性就是待着不动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.87,0:16:29.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my people are sedentary
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.50,0:16:31.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你光坐在家里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:31.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just sitting in your house?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.52,0:16:33.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就不会寂寞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:33.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ain't you going to get lonesome?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.22,0:16:34.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:34.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won't be lonesome
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.40,0:16:36.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我所有挚友都在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.40,0:16:36.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got all the friends I need here
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.55,0:16:37.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位是硬币
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:37.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is Penny
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.77,0:16:39.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有薯片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.77,0:16:39.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And Chip
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.40,0:16:42.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有问候一下用过的纸巾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.40,0:16:42.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And say hello to Used Napkin
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.43,0:16:45.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王的工作你要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:45.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How are you going to keep your job at the Krusty Krab?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.31,0:16:46.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.31,0:16:46.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No problem
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.53,0:16:53.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用特别长的锅铲就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:53.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A really long spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.49,0:16:55.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃东西怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:55.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about eating?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.56,0:16:56.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可是海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.56,0:16:56.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.65,0:16:57.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滤食就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.65,0:16:57.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just filter-feed
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.17,0:17:11.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你迟早得出门
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:10.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, sooner or later
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:11.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're going to have to go outside
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.96,0:17:13.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好  我都说了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:13.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen, I told you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.12,0:17:15.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我绝对不会再出家门一步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.12,0:17:15.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that I'm never leaving my house again
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.01,0:17:16.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝对不会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:16.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never-ever?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.30,0:17:18.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝对绝对不会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:18.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never-ever-ever
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.39,0:17:21.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝对绝对绝对永远不会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.39,0:17:21.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never-never-ever-ever for never-ever?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.62,0:17:24.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝对绝对绝对绝对永远永远不会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:24.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never-ever-never-never, ever-ever-never
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.02,0:17:27.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝对绝对绝对绝对绝对绝对不会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:27.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never-ever-ever- ever-ever-ever-ever-ever?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.97,0:17:31.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝对绝对绝对不会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.97,0:17:31.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never-ever-never-ever
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.33,0:17:33.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  说够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.33,0:17:33.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, Patrick, that is enough
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.77,0:17:36.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,薯片  能麻烦你送这两位到门口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.77,0:17:36.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chip, would you mind showing these two to the door?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.35,0:17:42.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  薯片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.35,0:17:42.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Chip
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.83,0:17:46.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来只能另外再交个好朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:46.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll have to find a new best friend
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.89,0:17:48.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:48.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.07,0:17:48.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.07,0:17:48.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.71,0:17:51.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:51.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.17,0:17:53.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非要让海绵宝宝出门不可
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:53.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll get SpongeBob to come outside
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.00,0:17:55.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让他知道根本没什么好怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:55.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and then he'll see there's nothing to be afraid of
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.72,0:17:57.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出了门马上就打他对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.72,0:17:57.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that's when I punch him, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.02,0:18:02.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看外面的水母啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.02,0:18:02.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at the jellyfish out here
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.93,0:18:07.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可惜海绵宝宝就要错过这么多乐趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:07.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too bad SpongeBob is missing out on all the fun
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.68,0:18:10.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,捉到一只了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.68,0:18:10.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I caught one
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.61,0:18:20.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看那些白痴冒生命危险去捉水母
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.61,0:18:20.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at those fools risking their lives jellyfishing
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.69,0:18:23.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过我这新爱好安全多了  对吧薯片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.69,0:18:23.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My new hobby is much safer, isn't it, Chip?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.05,0:18:24.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,捉灰尘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.05,0:18:24.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dust collecting
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.20,0:18:30.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像捉到一粒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.20,0:18:30.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I caught one
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.38,0:18:32.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得换点别的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:32.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got to try something else
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.07,0:18:34.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢呼三声
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.07,0:18:34.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Three cheers
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.16,0:18:36.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,庆祝你生日  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:36.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On your birthday, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.05,0:18:38.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢呼三声庆祝你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:38.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Three cheers for you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.52,0:18:41.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来吹蜡烛许愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.52,0:18:41.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, you've got to blow out the candles and make a wish
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.30,0:18:42.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不用许愿  硬币
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:42.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't need the wish, Penny
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.95,0:18:45.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想要的一切都在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.95,0:18:45.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything I could ever want is right here
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.47,0:18:47.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不如来唱咱们原创的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:47.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In fact, let's sing our own song
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.51,0:18:50.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就唱待在屋里有多快活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.51,0:18:50.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,about the joy of staying indoors
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.02,0:18:55.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道一个地方  保你平安不受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:55.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know of a place where you never get harmed
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.85,0:19:01.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个神奇地方  有着神奇魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:19:01.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A magical place with magical charms
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.30,0:19:05.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,屋里  屋里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:05.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Indoors, indoors
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.32,0:19:08.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,屋里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.32,0:19:08.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,indoors
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.70,0:19:10.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接着唱  硬币
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.70,0:19:10.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take it away, Penny
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.42,0:19:15.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,硬币的歌声简直是天籁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:15.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That Penny has the most beautiful voice
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.00,0:19:17.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是够了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:17.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is it, SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.22,0:19:19.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们一定要找到特别好玩的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:19.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going to find something that's so dang fun
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.97,0:19:21.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让你非出门不可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:21.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that you'll have to come outside
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.12,0:19:24.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蹦床
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:24.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Trampoline
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.55,0:19:25.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:25.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ice cream
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.64,0:19:27.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海底冲浪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:27.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Underwater surfing
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.68,0:19:29.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两个冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:29.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two ice creams
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.06,0:19:30.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摩天轮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:30.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ferris wheel
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.10,0:19:31.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是两个冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:31.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Still two ice creams
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.92,0:19:33.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟蛤蜊摔跤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.92,0:19:33.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Clam wrestling
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.40,0:19:35.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给老人家洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:35.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Washing an old person
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.55,0:19:37.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  那个不好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:37.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, that's not fun
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.07,0:19:38.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:38.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is for me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.27,0:19:44.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都不行  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.27,0:19:44.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing's working, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.97,0:19:46.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.97,0:19:46.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.57,0:19:48.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.57,0:19:48.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I say we take a bath
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.72,0:19:49.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.72,0:19:49.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.82,0:19:51.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能不能给我走开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:51.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you get out of here?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.23,0:19:55.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.23,0:19:55.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, remember
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.30,0:19:57.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等我发信号再跳出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.30,0:19:57.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,don't jump out until I give the signal
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.50,0:19:58.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:19:58.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.22,0:20:03.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  算你赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:03.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, SpongeBob, you win
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.77,0:20:05.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你永远待在家里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.77,0:20:05.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stay inside forever
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.47,0:20:08.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你意志简直跟钢铁一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:08.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yours is truly the iron will
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.00,0:20:09.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,趁现在  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:09.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, Pat
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.49,0:20:13.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有只大猩猩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.49,0:20:13.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A gorilla
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.95,0:20:15.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救救我啊  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.95,0:20:15.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Save me, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.27,0:20:21.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.27,0:20:21.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, guys, really
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.70,0:20:23.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这次的尝试最可悲了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.70,0:20:23.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is your saddest attempt yet
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.70,0:20:25.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就连薯片都知道那是派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:25.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even Chip knows that's Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.43,0:20:27.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,穿着去年万圣节穿过的扮装服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.43,0:20:27.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the same costume he wore for Halloween last year
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.97,0:20:29.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:29.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, really
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.84,0:20:31.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一定要来救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.84,0:20:31.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got to come save me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.70,0:20:32.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:32.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.00,0:20:34.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你朋友谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:34.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who's your friend?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.37,0:20:34.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:34.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.37,0:20:37.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是你应该要穿着猩猩服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.37,0:20:37.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you're supposed to be in the gorilla suit
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.35,0:20:39.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就穿着猩猩服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.35,0:20:39.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am in the gorilla suit
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.72,0:20:42.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我明明干得还行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:42.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought I was doing a pretty good job
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.97,0:20:45.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然你是派大星  那他是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:45.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you're Patrick, then who's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.04,0:20:50.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的是大猩猩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.04,0:20:50.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A real gorilla
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.82,0:21:05.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:05.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.71,0:21:12.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.71,0:21:12.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.58,0:21:17.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不可能的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:17.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This can't be happening
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.24,0:21:26.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我说的简直一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.24,0:21:26.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is exactly the kind of thing I was talking about
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.87,0:21:29.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正是他们自找的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.87,0:21:29.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, they were asking for it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.60,0:21:33.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都警告过他们外面多危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:31.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not like I didn't warn them
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:33.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,about the dangers of outside
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.58,0:21:34.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  薯片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.58,0:21:34.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Chip
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.36,0:21:37.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道他俩是我全世界最亲近的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.36,0:21:37.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know they're my two dearest friends in the whole world
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.31,0:21:40.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我都说过了  不管怎样我都不出门
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:40.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I told them I wasn't going outside no matter what
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.44,0:21:41.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不人身攻击也行的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:41.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can do without the name-calling
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.91,0:21:43.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多谢你了  用过的纸巾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.91,0:21:43.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,thank you very much, Used Napkin
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.24,0:21:45.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  薯片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:45.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know, Chip
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.30,0:21:47.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果我被大猩猩装进袋子里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.30,0:21:47.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if it was me out there bagged by an ape
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.98,0:21:50.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星跟珊迪肯定会不惜代价救我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.98,0:21:50.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick and Sandy would risk anything to save me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.20,0:21:54.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也一定要不惜代价救他们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:54.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I've got to do the same for them
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.67,0:21:56.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是我回不来  薯片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.67,0:21:56.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I don't come back, Chip
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.90,0:21:58.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,照顾小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.90,0:21:58.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,take good care of Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.38,0:22:02.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.38,0:22:02.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.52,0:22:03.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.52,0:22:03.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,here I go
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.80,0:22:05.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,离开家里安全的舒适圈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:05.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from the safety of my home
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.12,0:22:07.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走向外面的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.12,0:22:07.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to the outside world
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.78,0:22:23.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要踏出第一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.78,0:22:23.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm taking my first step
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.91,0:22:25.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,目前平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.91,0:22:25.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So far so good
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.85,0:22:27.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我应该能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.85,0:22:27.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I can do this
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.52,0:22:29.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.52,0:22:29.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.50,0:22:31.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的海神王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.50,0:22:31.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.10,0:22:32.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快弄下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.10,0:22:32.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get off of me
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.90,0:22:34.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快弄下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.90,0:22:34.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get off of me
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.08,0:22:35.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,薯片  救命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.08,0:22:35.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chip, help me
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.29,0:22:35.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.29,0:22:35.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,help me
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.82,0:22:42.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.82,0:22:42.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm still alive
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.27,0:22:45.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.27,0:22:45.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.50,0:22:47.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我成功出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.50,0:22:47.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I made it outside
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.02,0:22:49.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么东西都没法阻止我了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.02,0:22:49.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing can stop me now
Dialogue: 1,0:22:50.43,0:22:52.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在回屋里还来得及吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.43,0:22:52.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is it too late to go back inside yet?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.01,0:22:54.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.01,0:22:54.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's too late
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.65,0:22:56.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.65,0:22:56.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:56.67,0:22:57.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.67,0:22:57.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:57.27,0:22:59.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.27,0:22:59.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.12,0:23:01.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  都是我害的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.12,0:23:01.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I caused all this
Dialogue: 1,0:23:01.30,0:23:03.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也不怕出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.30,0:23:03.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not scared of going outside anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.24,0:23:06.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我怕大猩猩了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.24,0:23:06.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'm terrified of gorillas now
Dialogue: 1,0:23:06.15,0:23:08.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事的  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.15,0:23:08.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's okay, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:23:08.12,0:23:09.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们也怕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.12,0:23:09.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,us, too
Dialogue: 1,0:23:09.32,0:23:11.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过知道我还不理解什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.32,0:23:11.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know what I don't understand, though?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:12.35,0:23:13.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.35,0:23:13.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:13.28,0:23:16.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大猩猩来海底干嘛来着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.28,0:23:16.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's a gorilla doing underwater in the first place?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:18.02,0:23:18.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.02,0:23:18.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:23:18.85,0:23:19.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这么问还真有点怪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.85,0:23:19.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's funny you should
Dialogue: 1,0:23:20.15,0:23:21.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.15,0:23:21.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, you see, the
Dialogue: 1,0:23:21.39,0:23:22.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乔治  我们穿帮了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.39,0:23:22.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,George, they're onto us
Dialogue: 1,0:23:23.92,0:23:25.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.92,0:23:25.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.68,0:23:35.85,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(678,388)}本集完
